--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
CHANGES
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
        o
    ____|____
   |         |  This file lists changes made to the Ansible role.
   |  _   _  |  The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and
   | [_] [_] |  formatted to allow easy grepping by scripts.
   |____~____|
    ___//__//   The fields are:
   /|     |/    B: bug
  //|_____|     F: feature
    _|| ||_     I: improvement
   (__| |__)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 0.14.0 (2016-05-21)
F: Add support for Ansible 2.0

* Version 0.13.1 (2016-04-23)
B: Ensure OpenNTPD is stopped on OpenBSD

* Version 0.13.0 (2016-04-09)
F: Add support for FreeBSD 10.3-RELEASE
F: Drop support for FreeBSD 10.2-RELEASE

* Version 0.12.0 (2016-04-02)
F: Add support for OpenBSD 5.9
F: Drop support for OpenBSD 5.8

* Version 0.11.0 (2016-02-29)
F: Add support for OS family 'OpenBSD'

* Version 0.10.0 (2016-01-21)
F: Drop support for OS family 'Gentoo'

* Version 0.9.5 (2015-11-17)
I: Add missing Ansible tags

* Version 0.9.4 (2015-08-23)
I: Improve Shell exit codes

* Version 0.9.3 (2015-03-05)
I: Minor script improvements

* Version 0.9.2 (2014-07-22)
B: Fix default value of variable 'ntp_monitor_mail_recipient'

* Version 0.9.1 (2015-02-03)
I: Improve NTP update script

* Version 0.9.0 (2014-12-25)
F: Update 'sntp' command for OS family 'Gentoo'

* Version 0.8.0 (2014-12-12)
F: Add support for OS family 'FreeBSD'
I: Various small Ansible and Jinja2 improvements

* Version 0.7.2 (2014-09-11)
I: Change license from 'GPLv2' to 'Simplified BSD License'

* Version 0.7.1 (2014-08-28)
I: Ensure Ansible role is OS agnostic

* Version 0.7.0 (2014-08-14)
F: Remove support for OS family 'RedHat'

* Version 0.6.5 (2014-08-14)
I: Improve conditional statements

* Version 0.6.4 (2014-07-28)
I: Minor script improvements

* Version 0.6.3 (2014-07-22)
B: Remove 'recurse' argument from directory remove task

* Version 0.6.2 (2014-07-16)
I: Improve filter for interval option

* Version 0.6.1 (2014-06-24)
I: Improve 'ntpdate' options

* Version 0.6.0 (2014-06-24)
F: Add monitor option

* Version 0.5.1 (2014-06-17)
I: Improve script

* Version 0.5.0 (2014-05-30)
F: Add interval option for the cronjob
B: Fix usage of 'from address' (sender) option of mailx
I: Improve information contained in mail subject and body

* Version 0.4.0 (2014-05-29)
F: Add mail monitoring options
I: Improve script overall

* Version 0.3.1 (2014-05-26)
B: Move file configuration from 'install' to 'enable' task

* Version 0.3.0 (2014-05-23)
I: Add 'common' dependency and support for 'common' script directory

* Version 0.2.0 (2014-05-22)
I: Manage 'ntp.conf' and 'step-tickers' even when running as cronjob

* Version 0.1.2 (2014-05-17)
B: Add missing 'ntpdate' dependency for RedHat and CentOS

* Version 0.1.1 (2014-05-10)
B: Add missing newline in Jinja2 template

* Version 0.1.0 (2014-03-28)
F: Initial release
